      "verse_key": "38:8",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "أَءُ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نز</tajweed>ِلَ عَلَيْهِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>ذِّكْرُ م<tajweed class=iqlab>ِنۢ ب</tajweed>َيْنِنَا‌ۚ بَلْ هُمْ فِى شَ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>كٍّ م</tajweed>ِّ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ذ</tajweed>ِكْرِى‌ۖ بَل لَّ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َا يَذُوقُو<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> عَذ<tajweed class=madda_permissible>َا</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>٨</span>"
    },
    {
