      "verse_key": "38:9",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "أَمْ عِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ند</tajweed>َهُمْ خَز<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓئِنُ رَحْمَةِ رَبِّكَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعَزِيزِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْوَهّ<tajweed class=madda_permissible>َا</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>٩</span>"
