      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "وَثَمُودُ وَقَوْمُ لُو<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>طٍ و</tajweed>َأَصْحَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>بُ لْــَٔيْكَةِ‌ۚ أُ<tajweed class=slnt>وْ</tajweed>لَ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>ـٰٓ</tajweed>ئِكَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَحْز<tajweed class=madda_permissible>َا</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed>ُ <span class=end>١٣</span>"
